\pm1\\
\pm1\\
\pm1\\
\pm1
\end{bmatrix}$
\end_inset

(
\begin_inset Formula $2^{d+2}$
\end_inset

) dichotomies, where 
\begin_inset Formula $\mathbf{y}$
